<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩٩٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6006">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يُوسُفَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1513">حُصَيْنِ بْنِ عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2238">سَالِمِ بْنِ أَبِي الْجَعْدِ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرِ بْنِ عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا إِذَا صَعِدْنَا كَبَّرْنَا وَإِذَا نَزَلْنَا سَبَّحْنَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>